  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<l>kēṭṭai yeṉṟā niṉṟai yeṉṟā</l>
<l>kāttai yeṉṟā kaṇṭai yeṉṟā</l>
<l>vaṉṟi yaṉaittu muṉṉilai yalvaḻi</l>
<l>muṉṉuṟak kiḷanta viyalpā kummē.</l>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ivai muṉṉaiya nāṉkumpōla viṉāvoṭupaṭātu vāḷātē niṉṟuḻi, ivaiyum acaiccollāy niṟkum eṉpatu karuttu.</p>
<p>muṉṉiṉṟavaṟṟu nilaimaiyalvaḻi yeṉpāṟ, 'muṉṉilai yalvaḻi' eṉṟāṟ eṉpatu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC426">
<l>'kēṭṭai, kēṭṭai'</l>
<l>'niṉṟai, niṉṟai'</l>
<l>'kāttai, kāttai'</l>
<l>'kaṇṭai, kaṇṭai'</l></lg>
<p>eṉa varum. ivaiyum kaṭṭuraikkaṇ varumiṭam aṟintu koḷka.</p>
<p>iṉi, ivai viṉāvoṭu paṭṭuḻiyāyakkāl acainilaiyākā eṉpatu.	(30)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

